tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Votes (
    vote_id INT,
    voter_id INT,
    candidate_id INT,
    vote_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (vote_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (voter_id) REFERENCES VotingResults(voter_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (candidate_id) REFERENCES Candidates(candidate_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Statistics (
    stats_id INT,
    total_votes INT,
    total_candidates INT,
    total_parties INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (stats_id)
);
